		<title>减肥最合适的水果（6种不可错过的应季减肥水果！）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/8324.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 22 Jul 2023 04:06:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[果蔬知识]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[应季]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[摄入]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[水果]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=8324</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[在秋天这个大丰收的季节 水果圈显得格外的热闹 水果们尽情展现着自己的美味 在营养含量上同样谁也不服谁 减脂是味 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">在秋天这个大丰收的季节</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">水果圈显得格外的热闹</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">水果们尽情展现着自己的美味</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">在营养含量上同样谁也不服谁</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">减脂是味蕾+减脂的双重福利</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">偏偏有许多人都忽视了它们</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">吃够水果有多重要？水果吃不够，竟然会缩短寿命！根据中国疾病预防控制中心慢性传染疾病预防中心的研究发现：</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">我国因水果摄入不足造成期望寿命损失为1.73岁。25岁以上（包括25岁）人群的总死因中，约15%是由于水果摄入不足导致的，归因死亡数为134.84万。</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">健康成年人每天应摄入200-350克新鲜水果。</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">另外，水果是膳食纤维、钾、镁、抗氧化剂和酚类物质的良好来源。吃好水果不但能</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">降低血压和胆固醇，还能预防心脑血管疾病和癌症等疾病。</span></strong><span style="color: green;">吃够水果简直太重要了！</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/f38a4963fb7ef268f53a4d21c3ed07d5.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">美味、应季、不易长胖</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">估计是很多胖友们的追求</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">今天一起来pick下</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">美味又助甩脂的秋季水果</span>吧</strong></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/e053e15eea96129dc175c09603c7eba1.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/25314e22c7b1134b6ab5279c286b68a3.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">秋高气爽的秋天，怎么能错过柚子呢？柚子含有丰富的维生素C、膳食纤维以及丰富的果酸。</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">产生饱腹感的同时，还能抑制食欲。</span></strong>另外，柚子的热量也比较低，妥妥的减肥友好水果。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ca4d9ed76c63cdebefde9c32a73a3476.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/d0e4a1509d427ef44396b6ddeef4d9d7.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">秋天是橘子丰收的季节。橘子中不仅富含维生素C和果酸，还富含一种叫辛弗林的酸味成分，</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">维持免疫力的同时，还能分解、燃烧体内积蓄的脂肪。</span></strong></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/77a7e5ef7c36409bd6399dbc6ab38196.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/75ef27f892c5b58e55e8cafbb54a2d49.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">口感独特的梨子富含膳食纤维，可以改善肠道环境，促进体内废物的排出。另外，</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">梨中还含有蛋白酶，可以促进人体对肉类的消化。</span></strong></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/eb112c1784b21ff17acd50ef303086c9.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/7b4c51cf05d70f2a133811b076cc8001.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">似乎哪个季节都可以吃到苹果，但苹果的最佳食用季节是9-11月，是秋季的应季水果~</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">苹果中含有果胶，可以抑制糖类吸收，调节肠道。</span></strong>苹果中的钾元素还可以帮助人体消除水肿。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/eea6757d28547fd41a0ad795683282e2.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/3e08f03d662abe56e9847d0db8eef743.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">身为“维C之王”的猕猴桃不但维生素C含量高，还含有膳食纤维，可以促进排便、改善便秘。猕猴桃中的</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">猕猴桃碱有助人体对肉的消化，可以促进能量代谢，防止脂肪堆积。</span></strong></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/a20daa9109c86138ec1559d08c25acda.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ad00ac4d35288c20109d17ca10ecc7ae.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">石榴含有丰富的维生素C和B族维生素，以及钾、钙等矿物质和果蔬纤维。</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">增加饱腹感的同时，还能帮我们排毒。</span></strong>另外，石榴还能调节人体内的水分，是理想的减肥食物。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/74317ceb5f3aa6f504967a05e2865157.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
			</item>
